data.description: Assumable 5.375% VA loan! Fully Furnished. You won’t want to miss this stunning 5 bedroom, 4.5 bathroom home with attached 2-car garage nestled in the sought-after Missouri Acres neighborhood on a spacious lot. With only 42 homes as a part of this exclusive community, this home provides a quiet oasis from the daily hustle and bustle. As you step through the front door of the home your eyes are drawn to the cathedral-height ceilings in the 2-story foyer that is filled with natural light which reflects off of the rich hardwood floors throughout the main level. To your left, you walk through double glass french doors into the formal dining room with sophisticated chair railing and crown molding throughout. Pass through the butler’s pantry to the gourmet kitchen. This kitchen is truly a chef’s dream with stainless steel appliances, stunning granite countertops, and a large prep island that provides all the storage and countertop space you could desire! The informal dining space is the perfect place for casual family meals you can enjoy while taking in the serene view from the floor-to-ceiling windows. The spacious living room invites you to relax with loved ones around the modern gas fireplace, the ideal place to be on chilly winter evenings. Walk up the sweeping staircase and you will pass by the conveniently placed laundry room and make your way through double doors to the luxurious primary bedroom suite. This expansive room features an elegant, tiered ceiling, ample closet storage and deluxe private en-suite bathroom with dual sink vanity, soaking tub, and glass shower stall. Two bedrooms with their own closet storage, share a jack and jill bathroom with a large, dual sink vanity that provides ample storage. An additional bedroom and hall bathroom complete this level. Make your way to the lower level of the home and discover even more space! This fully-finished, walkout level features a massive recreation room as well as another full bathroom and bedroom - perfect for guest accommodations! Conveniently located near the new Southern Area Aquatics and Recreation Complex (SAARC) building, and only minutes from shopping and dining options - this home truly gives you a getaway retreat while still in close proximity to modern conveniences. All furniture conveys in the sale of the home (including TVs). Don’t miss the chance to make this beautiful home your own!
